 **Upgrad AI Agent – Content Repurposer**

 An AI-powered workflow built with **Lindy AI** to repurpose and localize educational content for *Upgrac EdTech Hackathon*

**\#\# 🎯 Problem Statement**

**AI-Powered Content Repurposing & Localization**  
Build a system that auto-transforms existing content (lectures, case studies, assignments) into multiple formats—short-form, regional languages, interactive quizzes—without requiring manual rework.

\#\# 💡 Our Solution  
The *Upgrad Content Repurposer Agent* automates the process by transforming **lectures, case studies, and assignments** into multiple formats instantly.  

✅ Key Features  
 **Social Media Post Generation** → Auto-create engaging content from lectures.    
 **Summary Generator** → Produce concise, learner-friendly summaries.    
 **Flashcard Generator** → Convert learning material into Q\&A flashcards.    
 **Content Localization** → Translate & adapt into \*\*regional languages\*\*.    
 **Google Drive Integration** → Automatically saves outputs in structured folders.

🚀 How It Works

1\. Upload content (lecture/case study as of now I have designed using free trail so instead of pdf paste text contect directly wich will consume less credits and for smooth execution)   
2\. Agent auto-generates:  
   \- Social posts    
   \- Summaries    
   \- Flashcards    
   \- Localized versions    
3\. Saves all results into Google Drive folders.
